            h2 Newsletters and tutorial videos
            p I’ve written newsletters for #[a(href='https://datamuse.com/') Datamuse], a search engine company that’s been around #[a(href='https://www.onelook.com/?c=trademark') since the early days of the web]. My job involved crawling through #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/') CivicSearch], a database that aggregates transcripts of local government meetings from the United States and Canada, to discuss important but below-the-radar issues.
            ul
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/fluoride') Fluoride in drinking water]
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/voter-turnout') Voter turnout]
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/ranked-choice-voting')] Ranked-choice voting
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/participatory-budgeting')] Participatory budgeting
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/rent-control')] Rent control
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/accessory-dwelling-units')] Accessory dwelling units
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/short-term-rentals')] Airbnbs and short-term rentals
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/immigration')] Immigration
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/cycling')] Cycling (#[a(href='https://pod.link/1800116578') podcast] and #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JVUH_MLu7SM') YouTube] video)
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/pickleball')] Pickleball
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/harm-reduction')] Harm reduction, the opioid crisis, and safe injection sites
                li #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/bus-rapid-transit')] Bus rapid transit
                li.starred #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/feature/absenteeism')] School absenteeism (and #[a(href='https://civicsearch.org/nsba_assets/chronic_absenteeism.pdf') one-pager])
            p I used Slack to communicate and GitHub to create web versions of the newsletter.
            p I also scripted, recorded, and edited one-minute tutorial videos for YouTube that demonstrated key features of OneLook, a dictionary–thesaurus–word-finder combo.
            ul
                li.starred #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oFz9OyLcy7k')] OneLook subject index
                li.starred #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a-HmvCyjrW0')] OneLook wildcard search patterns
                li.starred #[a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Eku7oJkxfTY')] OneLook result tabs
