            h2 Guideline documents
            p From June 2021 to June 2023, I served as the internal chair of the Isla Vista Community Relations Committee (IVCRC), a student philanthropic and event-planning organization under the Associated Students of UC Santa Barbara. To make sure everyone knew what they were doing—and to create an institutional knowledge that could be expanded upon by future members—I wrote more than 25 guideline documents of 2 to 4 pages in length. Below is a small selection.
            ul
                li Honoraria guidelines
                li Publicity guidelines
                li Communication guidelines
                li Meeting guidelines
                li Pardall Center guidelines
        section
