            h2 Newspaper articles
            p From October 2019 to April 2023, I contributed news articles and opinion pieces to the Daily Nexus, UC Santa Barbara’s primary student newspaper. I interviewed students and community members and reported on local happenings, in the process working closely with the editors of each respective section.
            p From my time here, I know how to ask effective questions and get to the point.
